OL,3,CLarge blaze 'devastating' at historic
OL,4,Cbuilding in Ballycastle
OL,6,FConcern has been voiced over a
OL,7,F"devastating" fire at a historic
OL,8,Fbuilding in Co Antrim.
OL,10,FAt its height 42 firefighters were
OL,11,Fbattling the blaze at the derelict
OL,12,Fbuilding at The Diamond in Ballycastle
OL,13,Fon Sunday night. They had left the
OL,14,Fscene on Monday morning.
OL,16,FA Northern Ireland Fire and Rescue
OL,17,FService (NIFRS) spokesperson said they
OL,18,Freceived a call about the incident
OL,19,Fshortly after 8pm on Sunday.
