OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1776704798
OL,3,CLarge blaze 'devastating' at historic
OL,4,Cbuilding in Ballycastle
OL,6,F42 firefighters came from stations in
OL,7,FBallycastle, Ballymoney and Portrush
OL,8,Fto assist. Two aerial appliances, one
OL,9,Ffrom Northland Station and one from
OL,10,FSpringfield Station, attended the
OL,11,Fincident along with a command support
OL,12,Funit from Kilrea Station.
OL,14,FLocal residents were advised to keep
OL,15,Fwindows and doors closed, and members
OL,16,Fof the public were asked to avoid the
OL,17,Farea to support firefighting
OL,18,Foperations.
