OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1776704798
OL,3,CLarge blaze 'devastating' at historic
OL,4,Cbuilding in Ballycastle
OL,6,FSinn Fein councillor Cara McShane said
OL,7,Fthe fire was at the Antrim Arms, a
OL,8,Fformer hotel, which she described as a
OL,9,F"cornerstone of heritage in the town".
OL,11,F"I am deeply concerned by the
OL,12,Fdevastating fire at the Antrim Arms in
OL,13,FBallycastle," she said.
OL,15,F"My immediate thoughts are with local
OL,16,Fresidents and businesses who will be
OL,17,Faffected by this incident.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@eO]sD@AOUuD@MO]wD@AOU
