OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1776704798
OL,3,CLarge blaze 'devastating' at historic
OL,4,Cbuilding in Ballycastle
OL,6,F"This is an historic building and a
OL,7,Fcornerstone of the heritage in the
OL,8,Ftown. However the wellbeing and safety
OL,9,Fof those living in the immediate
OL,10,Fvicinity is my main concern right now."
